column1: Title: Oral Cancer at HPV-Related Sites in White Males

Description: SEER 9 Registries Databases, November 2011 Submission. HPV-related sites are base of tongue, lingual tonsil, palatine tonsil, oropharynx, and Waldeyer's ring. ICD-O-3 Topography Codes C019, C024, C090-099, C100-109, and C142.
